<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.4">
<l>vaṇanaṉ ṟuṭaiya vayirak kaṭippiṭṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">vārkātu tāḻap perukkik</l>
<l>kuṇanaṉ ṟuṭaiyarik kōpāla piḷḷaikaḷ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvintā nīcolluk koḷḷā</l>
<l>yiṇainaṉ ṟaḻakiya vikkaṭip piṭṭā</l>
<l rend="indent">liṉiya palāppaḻan tantu</l>
<l>cuṇanaṉ ṟaṇimulai yuṇṇat taruvaṉnāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">cōttam pirāṉiṅkē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These cowherding children, who have good qualities,</l>
<l>have put diamond earrings that have a beautiful hue</l>
<l rend="indent">filling their long ears so that they hang down,</l>
<l>[but] you, O Govinda!, do not heed [my] words.</l>
<l>If [you let me] put this very beautiful pair of earrings [in your ear],</l>
<l>I will give [you] sweet jack-fruit and</l>
<l rend="indent">[my] breast well adorned with a golden powder to drink.</l>
<l>Praise to you O Lord! Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
